â”‚   â”œâ”€â”€ TeacherManager.php     â† Manage teacher user creation/retrieval
â”‚   â”œâ”€â”€ ClassManager.php       â† Manage CPT ld\_class
â”‚   â””â”€â”€ StudentManager.php     â† Handle optional student creation
